  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/b7b4999f49e8efc21f4ce243eae91a07.poster.avif?t=1746371581\" width=624 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/b7b4999f49e8efc21f4ce243eae91a07.webm?t=1746371581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/b7b4999f49e8efc21f4ce243eae91a07.mp4?t=1746371581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose your Guardian!</strong></h2></li></ul>Unleash the power of a diverse roster, each with unique abilities and elemental special moves. Trade your hard-earned spoils to unlock powerful new skills and master an array of devastating weapons.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/d3486e9ff2b12c4a5f73b5d42732c565.avif?t=1746371581\" width=620 height=232 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Advance your combat!</strong></h2></li></ul>Explore diverse weapon styles, unlock unique character traits, and harness the elemental power of Gaia. Adapt on the fly by switching weapons mid-battle to change the tide of the fight.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/c95f0c2ba3286f8bc3c78242d31058c7.poster.avif?t=1746371581\" width=624 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/c95f0c2ba3286f8bc3c78242d31058c7.webm?t=1746371581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/c95f0c2ba3286f8bc3c78242d31058c7.mp4?t=1746371581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Master the Arena!</strong></h2></li></ul>Leverage the environment for a tactical edge. Each Arena evolves with the action, offering varied routes, strategic choke points, and shortcuts to unlock. Coordinate with your team and use your mobility to dominate the battlefield..<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/12b01e2bcc8ce2af5776c8fcd2d20437.avif?t=1746371581\" width=620 height=522 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Become Guardian. Become Gaia.</strong></h2></li></ul><br>Handmade by a solo developer. Engine included.<br>Enhanced for Steam Deck.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/b7b4999f49e8efc21f4ce243eae91a07.poster.avif?t=1746371581\" width=624 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/b7b4999f49e8efc21f4ce243eae91a07.webm?t=1746371581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/b7b4999f49e8efc21f4ce243eae91a07.mp4?t=1746371581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose your Guardian!</strong></h2></li></ul>Unleash the power of a diverse roster, each with unique abilities and elemental special moves. Trade your hard-earned spoils to unlock powerful new skills and master an array of devastating weapons.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/d3486e9ff2b12c4a5f73b5d42732c565.avif?t=1746371581\" width=620 height=232 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Advance your combat!</strong></h2></li></ul>Explore diverse weapon styles, unlock unique character traits, and harness the elemental power of Gaia. Adapt on the fly by switching weapons mid-battle to change the tide of the fight.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/c95f0c2ba3286f8bc3c78242d31058c7.poster.avif?t=1746371581\" width=624 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/c95f0c2ba3286f8bc3c78242d31058c7.webm?t=1746371581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/c95f0c2ba3286f8bc3c78242d31058c7.mp4?t=1746371581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Master the Arena!</strong></h2></li></ul>Leverage the environment for a tactical edge. Each Arena evolves with the action, offering varied routes, strategic choke points, and shortcuts to unlock. Coordinate with your team and use your mobility to dominate the battlefield..<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/12b01e2bcc8ce2af5776c8fcd2d20437.avif?t=1746371581\" width=620 height=522 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Become Guardian. Become Gaia.</strong></h2></li></ul><br>Handmade by a solo developer. Engine included.<br>Enhanced for Steam Deck.",
